          <title>
            <string language="en">Planting Seeds and Identifying Plant Parts</string>
            <string language="es">Plantación de semillas e identificación de las partes de las plantas</string>
            <string language="ga">Síolta a chur agus Páirteanna Plandaí a Aithint</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Startwerte für Zufallsgenerator und das 
Kennzeichnen der Betriebsteile errichten</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Plantant des graines et identifier des pièces 
d'usine</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Plantando sementes e identificar as peças da

            <string language="x-mt-el">Φύτευση των σπόρων και προσδιορισμός των μερών 
εγκαταστάσεων</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Focuses on planting seeds, observing growth and identifying plant parts and their functions. Includes four activities.</string>
            <string language="es">Se centra en la plantación de semillas, se observa el crecimiento y se identifican las partes de las plantas y sus funciones. Incluye cuatro actividades.</string>
            <string language="ga">Díríonn sé ar síolta a chur, breathnú ar fhás agus páirteanna plandaí agus a bhfeidhmeanna a aithint. Áirítear ceithre ghníomhaíocht leis.</string>
          </description>
          <language>en</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">SESE Science</string>
            <string language="es">Ciencias SESE. Elementos vivos. Plan de lección</string>
            <string language="ga">OSIE Eolaíocht</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Living Things</string>
            <string language="ga">Nithe Beo</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Lesson Plan</string>
            <string language="ga">Plean Ceachta</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Foki auf dem Errichten der Startwerte für 
Zufallsgenerator, dem Beobachten des Wachstums und dem Kennzeichnen 
der Betriebsteile und ihrer Funktionen. Schließt vier 
Aktivitäten ein.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Foyers sur planter des graines, observer la 
croissance et identifier des pièces d'usine et leurs fonctions. 
Inclut quatre activités.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Focos em plantar sementes, em observar o 
crescimento e em identificar as peças da planta e as suas funções. 
Inclui quatro atividades.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Fuochi sulla piantatura dei semi, 
sull'osservazione dello sviluppo e sull'identificare le parti della 
pianta e le loro funzioni. Include quattro attività.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εστίαση στη φύτευση των σπόρων, την παρατήρηση της 
αύξησης και τον προσδιορισμό των μερών εγκαταστάσεων και των 
λειτουργιών τους. Περιλαμβάνει τέσσερις δραστηριότητες.</string>
